sc_cat_item.description:
This leverages GenAI capabilities to provide recommendations on optimal database structure, following ServiceNow best practices.

Deliverables:

  • Excel VBA Script to create an Excel file with complete data model details to support application build using App Engine
  • Mermaid code to provide visualization of all tables and relationships
  • Build blueprint documenting recommendations

Benefits:

  • Reduced effort for application modeling
  • Data model blueprint jumpstarts development
  • Visual mapping of optimal table relationships
  • Leverages NOW best practices to enhance quality
